Pakistan Zindabaad

Tears filled my eyes as I listened to this soulful anthem, each note echoing the love and sacrifice that built our beloved homeland. 
May Allah Almighty protect Pakistan, strengthen it with unity, and guide it on the path of true prosperity until the very end of time. 
Long live Pakistan — our pride, our identity, our eternal home. 🇵🇰 14th August 2025 — Pakistan Zindabad!
